4)" }}{PARA 0 "" 0 "" {TEXT -1 97 "b.regions (intervals) in the domain
 of the function where the values of the function are positive" }}
{PARA 0 "" 0 "" {TEXT -1 0 "" }}{PARA 0 "" 0 "" {TEXT -1 33 "[-infinit
y.. 2], [4.. +infinity ]" }}{PARA 0 "" 0 "" {TEXT -1 0 "" }}{PARA 0 "
" 0 "" {TEXT -1 97 "c.regions (intervals) in the domain of the functio
n where the values of the function are negative" }}{PARA 0 "" 0 "" 
